   A Dassault Mirage F1 CT (right) was on display as Airborne Tactical
   Advantage Company (ATAC), part of Textron Airborne Solutions, broke
   ground on the Adversarial Center of Excellence at Alliance Airport in
   Fort Worth, Thursday, October 11, 2018. ATAC plans on purchasing more
   than 60 of the Dassault Aviation built air force planes that have
